**Running a single bag file:** //Change path provided to your relative path
rosrun rosbag_filter rosbag_filter_node --ros_version ros1 --start_time 10 --end_time 20 --bag_file ~/catkin_ws/bags/bag_01.bag --topics "/imu/data /front_camera/image_raw"

**Running a folder of bag files:** 
rosrun rosbag_filter rosbag_filter_node --ros_version ros1 --start_time 10 --end_time 20 --bag_folder ~/catkin_ws/bags --topics "/imu/data /front_camera/image_raw"

**Full bag duration for one file:** //Simply delete start and end time from specifications: 
rosrun rosbag_filter rosbag_filter_node --ros_version ros1 --bag_file ~/catkin_ws/bags/bag_01.bag --topics "/imu/data /front_camera/image_raw"

**Full duration for folder of bag files:** 
rosrun rosbag_filter rosbag_filter_node --ros_version ros1 --bag_folder ~/catkin_ws/bags --topics "/imu/data /front_camera/image_raw"

**For specification on topic list:** //Change path to your relative path
rosbag info ~/catkin_ws/bags/filtered_bag_01.bag 

**To Run all topics:**
rosrun rosbag_filter rosbag_filter_node --ros_version ros1 --start_time 10 --end_time 20 --bag_file ~/catkin_ws/bags/bag_01.bag --topics "/imu/data /front_camera/image_raw /navsat/odom /radar/radar_image_far"



Summary of Parameters
--ros_version: Specifies the ROS version (ros1 or ros2).
--start_time: The start time for filtering (in seconds).
--end_time: The end time for filtering (in seconds).
--bag_file: The path to the ROS bag file.
--topics: The topics to include in the filtered bag, separated by spaces.
